---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="bg-bg-light py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mb-16">
      <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.5em] text-olive uppercase">PHOTO STRIP</span>
      <h2 class="mt-5 text-[clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.8rem)] font-bold text-primary">포토 스트립 디자인</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-secondary max-w-xl">
        40종 이상의 웨딩 포토 스트립 디자인 중 선택하실 수 있습니다.<br />
        직접 디자인을 제작하셔도 적용이 가능합니다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Template preview images from PDF -->
    <div class="gs-stagger space-y-4">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border-light">
        <img
          src={`${base}/images/wedding/templates-1.jpg`}
          alt="포토 스트립 디자인 - Handwriting, Simple, Rounded"
          class="w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border-light">
          <img
            src={`${base}/images/wedding/templates-2.jpg`}
            alt="포토 스트립 디자인 - Full, Clean, Comic, Always, Four cut"
            class="w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border-light">
          <img
            src={`${base}/images/wedding/templates-3.jpg`}
            alt="포토 스트립 디자인 - Analog, Landscape, Thanks, Just love, Manuscript"
            class="w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-secondary text-center">
      위 디자인 외에도 다양한 디자인이 준비되어 있습니다. 셀프 디자인도 가능합니다.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Backdrop Section -->
<section class="bg-white py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-20">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="gs-slide-left">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.5em] text-olive uppercase">BACKDROP</span>
        <h2 class="mt-5 text-[clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.8rem)] font-bold leading-tight text-primary">
          백드롭 선택
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-6 h-[2px] w-10 bg-olive"></div>
        <p class="mt-8 text-base leading-relaxed text-secondary">
          사진 배경으로 사용될 백드롭을 선택하실 수 있습니다.
          시퀸 백드롭 2종과 화이트 커튼 백드롭 4종, 총 6가지 옵션을 제공합니다.
          백드롭을 사용하지 않고 웨딩홀 벽면을 배경으로 활용하는 것도 가능합니다.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-secondary">
            <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-olive/10 text-olive text-xs">✓</span>
            백드롭 사이즈: 폭 2,100mm × 높이 2,000mm
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-secondary">
            <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-olive/10 text-olive text-xs">✓</span>
            촬영 공간 약 2m × 2m 필요
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-secondary">
            <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-olive/10 text-olive text-xs">✓</span>
            야외 웨딩도 설치 가능 (사전 협의)
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Diagram image -->
      <div class="gs-slide-right overflow-hidden rounded-2xl">
        <img
          src={`${base}/images/wedding/backdrop-diagram.jpg`}
          alt="백드롭 설치 구성도"
          class="w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Backdrop options showcase -->
    <div class="gs-fade-up mt-16">
      <h3 class="mb-8 text-center text-lg font-semibold text-primary">백드롭 6종 옵션</h3>
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border-light bg-white">
        <img
          src={`${base}/images/wedding/backdrop-options.jpg`}
          alt="백드롭 옵션 - 골드 시퀸, 로즈골드 시퀸, 화이트 커튼 플라워 가랜드 4종"
          class="w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-center text-xs text-secondary sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6">
        <span class="rounded-full bg-bg-light px-3 py-1.5">골드 시퀸</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-bg-light px-3 py-1.5">로즈골드 시퀸</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-bg-light px-3 py-1.5">플라워 가랜드 A</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-bg-light px-3 py-1.5">플라워 가랜드 B</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-bg-light px-3 py-1.5">위스테리아</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-bg-light px-3 py-1.5">화이트 로즈</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Backdrop detail close-ups -->
    <div class="gs-stagger mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border-light">
        <img
          src={`${base}/images/wedding/backdrop-flower-garland.jpg`}
          alt="화이트 커튼 백드롭 - 플라워 가랜드"
          class="w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border-light">
        <img
          src={`${base}/images/wedding/backdrop-wisteria.jpg`}
          alt="화이트 커튼 백드롭 - 위스테리아"
          class="w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Outdoor wedding example -->
    <div class="gs-scale-in mt-8 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl">
      <img
        src={`${base}/images/wedding/outdoor-setup.jpg`}
        alt="야외 웨딩 포토부스 세팅"
        class="h-[350px] w-full object-cover lg:h-[450px]"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
